  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Baobab</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Baobab</application> package contains a graphical
      directory tree analyzer.
    </para>

    &lfs91_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
